					<description><![CDATA[I guess I&#039;m somewhat opposite.  If someone directly criticizes something I&#039;m working on - be it housework or graphic design or personal fashion - I&#039;m more likely to work against them MORE.  If they hadn&#039;t said anything, then I&#039;ll just chug along until I get bored or distracted.  

But if someone says, &quot;I hate the way you ____, and you shouldn&#039;t do that,&quot; I immediately go into &quot;Oh YEAH!!  Well, I&#039;ll show YOU!!!&quot; mode.  (My entire family is like this.  If we&#039;re left alone, we just sort of vegetate.  If we get insulted or harshly criticized, we go into extreme &quot;Watch me as I SOAR!!&quot; mode.  lol )]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I guess I&#8217;m somewhat opposite.  If someone directly criticizes something I&#8217;m working on &#8211; be it housework or graphic design or personal fashion &#8211; I&#8217;m more likely to work against them MORE.  If they hadn&#8217;t said anything, then I&#8217;ll just chug along until I get bored or distracted.  </p>
<p>But if someone says, &#8220;I hate the way you ____, and you shouldn&#8217;t do that,&#8221; I immediately go into &#8220;Oh YEAH!!  Well, I&#8217;ll show YOU!!!&#8221; mode.  (My entire family is like this.  If we&#8217;re left alone, we just sort of vegetate.  If we get insulted or harshly criticized, we go into extreme &#8220;Watch me as I SOAR!!&#8221; mode.  lol )</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
